{
  "groups": [
    {
      "title": "Installation",
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "install_title",
          "label": "Getting Started",
          "icon": "rocket",
          "content": "## Welcome!\n\n**Welcome to ZYNQ!**\n\nThis library provides hundreds of games with rich metadata and thumbnails, alongside a robust WebRTC-powered real-time communication system.\n\nChoose your preferred way to install the library below."
        },
        {
          "id": "install_script",
          "label": "Script Tag",
          "icon": "code",
          "content": "### Script Tag\n\nUse this for the fastest setup via CDN.\n\n```html\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/un-zynq/zynq-lib@1.0.9/index.min.js\"></script>\n```"
        },
        {
          "id": "install_module",
          "label": "ES Module",
          "icon": "package",
          "content": "### ES Module\n\nFor modern JavaScript projects (Vite, Webpack, etc).\n\n```javascript\nimport \"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/un-zynq/zynq-lib@1.0.9/index.min.js\"\n```"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "ZYNQ Games",
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "games_object",
          "label": "Game Object",
          "icon": "gamepad-2",
          "content": "## ZYNQ.games\n### Game Object\n\nA game object returned by `ZYNQ.games` methods.\n\n```text\nGame:\n- name: string\n- category?: string\n- alias: string\n- url: string\n- thumb: string\n- devices?: number[]\n\nComputed:\n- isSupported: boolean\n- isFavorite: boolean\n```"
        },
        {
          "id": "games_properties",
          "label": "Properties",
          "icon": "database",
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "games_prop_list",
              "label": "list",
              "content": "### ZYNQ.games.list\n```javascript\nZYNQ.games.list\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_prop_total",
              "label": "total",
              "content": "### ZYNQ.games.total\n```javascript\nZYNQ.games.total\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_prop_filtered",
              "label": "filteredCount",
              "content": "### ZYNQ.games.filteredCount\n```javascript\nZYNQ.games.filteredCount\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_prop_history",
              "label": "history",
              "content": "### ZYNQ.games.getHistory()\n```javascript\nZYNQ.games.getHistory()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_prop_favorites",
              "label": "favorites",
              "content": "### ZYNQ.games.favorites\n```javascript\nZYNQ.games.favorites\n```"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "ZYNQ Peer",
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "peer_constructor",
          "label": "Constructor & Singleton",
          "icon": "plug",
          "content": "## ZYNQ.peer / ZYNQPeer\n\n### Create a Peer\n\nWrapper around PeerJS with data + media + reconnect logic.\n\n```javascript\nconst peer = new ZYNQ.Peer({ video: true, audio: true, txt: true })\n```"
        },
        {
          "id": "peer_methods",
          "label": "Methods",
          "icon": "cog",
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "peer_connect",
              "label": ".connect(id)",
              "content": "### connect(id)\n```javascript\npeer.connect(\"id\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_send",
              "label": ".send(id, data)",
              "content": "### send(id, data)\n```javascript\npeer.send(\"id\", \"hello\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_call",
              "label": ".call(id)",
              "content": "### call(id)\n```javascript\npeer.call(\"id\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_disconnect",
              "label": ".disconnect(id)",
              "content": "### disconnect(id)\n\nCloses BOTH data + media connection and disables auto-reconnect for that peer.\n\n```javascript\npeer.disconnect(\"id\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_close",
              "label": ".close()",
              "content": "### close()\n\nCloses all connections but keeps instance alive.\n\n```javascript\npeer.close()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_destroy",
              "label": ".destroy()",
              "content": "### destroy()\n\nFully destroys peer instance.\n\n```javascript\npeer.destroy()\n```"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "peer_events",
          "label": "Events",
          "icon": "radio",
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "peer_event_ready",
              "label": "ready",
              "content": "### ready\n```javascript\npeer.on(\"ready\", id => {})\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_event_open",
              "label": "open",
              "content": "### open\nFired when a DATA connection is opened with a remote peer.\n```javascript\npeer.on(\"open\", id => {})\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_event_message",
              "label": "message",
              "content": "### message\n```javascript\npeer.on(\"message\", msg => {})\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_event_stream",
              "label": "stream",
              "content": "### stream\n```javascript\npeer.on(\"stream\", data => {})\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_event_close",
              "label": "close",
              "content": "### close\n```javascript\npeer.on(\"close\", data => {})\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_event_reconnecting",
              "label": "reconnecting",
              "content": "### reconnecting\n```javascript\npeer.on(\"reconnecting\", data => {})\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "peer_event_error",
              "label": "error",
              "content": "### error\n```javascript\npeer.on(\"error\", err => {})\n```"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
